sections.Remastered version:
- In order to promote Movie 28: One-eyed Flashback, which shares similar elements such as "Kansuke Yamato & Yui Uehara", a remastered version of this case will be aired over the span of March 22 and 29; April 5, 2025. Incidentally, the actual movie will premiere on April 18, 2025.
- "The Mysterious Armored Warrior" arc, formerly produced as 1 Hour Special, was re-edited into two separate episodes, denoted by "1" and "2" respectively:
Furinkazan - The Mysterious Armored Warrior 1 (風林火山 迷宮の鎧武者 壱 ,Fūrinkazan Meikyū no Yoroimusha Ichi?);
Furinkazan - The Mysterious Armored Warrior 2 (風林火山 迷宮の鎧武者 弐 ,Fūrinkazan Meikyū no Yoroimusha Ni?).
